</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1189,2077]" pageId="2" pageNumber="13">
1a Forewing ground colour white ................................................................................................................................. 3 1b Forewing ground colour not white ........................................................................................................................... 2 2a Forewing ground colour yellow ............................................................................................................................... 5 2b Forewing ground colour ochre brown; hindwing brown suffused white basally; male genitalia with juxta u-shaped and phallus clearly divided into two parts ....................................................................................... 
<taxonomicName box="[1252,1370,1317,1341]" class="Insecta" family="Crambidae" genus="Aurotalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dicksoni" status="sp. n.">
